### Producer {#afb5f97c61a632d45eaa7ddf0cfe87e72}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="Str llvm::irsymtab::storage::Header::Producer">
The producer&#39;s version string (LLVM&#95;VERSION&#95;STRING &quot; &quot; LLVM&#95;REVISION).

Consumers should rebuild the symbol table from IR if the producer&#39;s version does not match the consumer&#39;s version due to potential differences in symbol table format, symbol enumeration order and so on.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/irsymtab-h/#l00145">145</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/irsymtab-h">IRSymtab.h</a>.

### Version {#a68715f91247eacbf700e7a1fbf783366}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="Word llvm::irsymtab::storage::Header::Version">
Version number of the symtab format.

This number should be incremented when the format changes, but it does not need to be incremented if a change to LLVM would cause it to create a different symbol table.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/irsymtab-h/#l00138">138</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/irsymtab-h">IRSymtab.h</a>.
